Interface IPipelineConnections

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    PipelineConnections, PipelineSpecification, PipelineSpecificationWithVersions
    public interface IPipelineConnections
extends IPipelineSpecificationBasic
    This interface caches IOutputConnection and ITransformationConnection objects required by an IPipelineSpecification.
